    public class TapControlImpl
extends BranchFlowControlImpl
implements TapControl
    An implementation of the model object 'Tap VControl'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Control Type
    • Tap Step Size
    • Tap Steps
    • Compensate Z
    • Vc Gen PV Bus
    • Vc Bus
